            <title>[SUREFIRE-1759] NullPointerException from RunEntryStatisticsMap#serialize when there&apos;s a class-level @Ignore annotation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1759</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a class with a class-level @Ignore annotation is run, the output looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;
